<br>
go to Freeport and make toolboxes.<br>
<br>
Groflah's forge has excellent supplies for this. Buy as much small ore as you can carry and make metal bits. Then go buy lots and lots of water. Using the forge outside, combine:<br>
<br>
1 metal bits<br>
1 water flask<br>
<br>
This yields a toolbox, which groflah's will reinburse you handsomely. A word of warning - a toolbox is considered a container, so you need to make some space for them.<br>
